Anonymous?  These people want us to believe that no organized entity is responsible?  Amazing.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>In the absence of any claim of responsibility,<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
