<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>the symbolic nature of the targets may have been assumed to be self-explanatory. The World Trade Center clearly symbolized U.S. global economic power, while the Pentagon represented U.S. military power.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
