<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Thus, it seems highly unlikely that the September 11 attacks were symbolically directed against &quot;American values&quot; as celebrated in the United States.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
