<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>According to reports, 15 of the 19 identified hijackers were Saudi Arabians hostile to the presence of U.S. military bases on Saudi soil.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
