<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>September 11 suggests that the nation projecting its power abroad is vulnerable at home, but the real issue is U.S. intervention abroad.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
