<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Indeed the Bush wars are designed precisely to defend and strengthen U.S. power abroad. It is U.S. global power projection that is being defended, not domestic freedoms and way of life.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
